<section class="membership-section">
    <div class="membership-container">
        <h2 class="membership-main-title">Our Membership Offers</h2>

        <div class="membership-grid">
            <div class="membership-card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="membership-icon-wrapper">
                        <img src="/images/icon-standard-membership.svg" alt="Icon">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Standard Membership</h3>
                    <p class="card-description">With the Standard Membership, get access to our full range of gym facilities.</p>
                    <ul class="membership-features">
                        <li>Standard Locker</li>
                        <li>High-energy group fitness classes</li>
                        <li>Motivating & supportive environment</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="membership-price-box">

                    <div class="price-info">
                        <span class="price-amount">495.00</span><span class="price-period">/monthly</span>
                        <p class="price-subtitle">* Monthly 20 Classes</p>
                      
                    </div>
                   
                    
                    <a href="#" class="btn-lime-join">Join Now <i class="arrow-icon-membership"></i></a>
                    


                    <p class="price-footer">Try Any Membership Fre for 1 Week</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="membership-card">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="membership-icon-wrapper">
                        <img src="/images/icon-premium-membership.svg" alt="Icon">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Premium Membership</h3>
                    <p class="card-description">With the Premium Membership, get access to our full range of gym facilities.</p>
                    <ul class="membership-features">
                        <li>Priority Support & Premium Locker</li>
                        <li>High-energy group fitness classes</li>
                        <li>Motivating & supportive environment</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="membership-price-box">
                    <div class="price-info">
                        <span class="price-amount">595.00</span><span class="price-period">/monthly</span>
                        <p class="price-subtitle">* Monthly 20 Classes</p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="#" class="btn-lime-join">Join Now <i class="arrow-icon-membership"></i></a>
                    <p class="price-footer">Try Any Membership Fre for 1 Week</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="membership-card dark-card">
                <div class="dark-card-content">
                    <h4>Get Your Membership</h4>
                    <p class="info-mebership">Our memberships give you access to all equipment, personalized training.</p>
                    <div class="call-action">
                        <h5>Call Us At: +(46) 8 410 521 00</h5>
                        <a href="#" class="btn-lime-rounded">Call Us Today!<i class="arrow-icon-membership"></i></a>
                    </div>
                    <img src="/images/our-pricing-fitness-women.svg" alt="Fitness Woman" class="card-person-img">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="membership-info-row">
            <span><i class="icon-calendar"></i> Get 30 day free trial</span>
            <span><i class="icon-payment"></i> No any hidden fees pay</span>
            <span><i class="icon-clock"></i> You can cancel anytime</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="faq-section-membership">

    <div class="faq-container-membership">

        <div class="photo-faq-left">
            <img src=" /images/faqs-image-fitness-man.svg" alt="Man Fitness" class="card-person-man-img" />


        </div>

        <div class="faq-accordion-membership">
            <span class="faq-badge">
                <span class="dot"></span>
                Frequently Asked Questions</span>
            <h2 class="faq-main-title">Common questions about gym and training</h2>

            <div class="accordion-container">
                <div class="accordion-item active">
                    <button class="accordion-header">
                        Q1. Do I need prior gym experience to Join CoreFitness?
                        <span class="arrow"></span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>No, GymPro is designed for all fitness levels. Our trainers guide beginners with proper techniques and structured workout plans to help them start safely and confidently.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Every new member receives a personalized introduction to equipments</li>
                            <li>Workouts are designed to grow with you, ensuring beginners can start safely.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-header">
                        Q2. What facilities are included with the membership?
                        <span class="arrow"></span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>Training with PT and group training</p>
                    </div>
                </div>


                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-header">
                        Q3. Can i try the gym  before i taking a  Membership?
                        <span class="arrow"></span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>Yes, everybody can try the gym one week for free.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>


                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-header">
                        Q4. Are there group workout programs availaable?
                        <span class="arrow"></span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>Yes, everybody can try the gym for one week for free<br/>
                            and includes groups workout too.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>


                
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <button class="accordion-header">
                        Q5. Is nustrition guidance includes in the plans.?
                        <span class="arrow"></span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="accordion-content">
                        <p>Yes, first  month its for free, after this period<br/>
                            its 50% less for 11 month for new clients.

                       </p>
                    </div>
                </div>




            </div>
        </div>


    </div>



</section>